metadata.name: Reppin NFT Pass WAGMI
metadata.description:
Reppin NFT Passes is the genesis collection from Reppin Pins. All Reppin NFT Passes come with a free pin: "GM", "HODL", "Probably Nothing", or "WAGMI". Shipping not included.  
 
Each pass carries these utilities:  
• Discounts on ReppinPins.com  
• Access to Reppin’s Discord  
• Early access to pin releases  
• Wholesale prices on Custom Pins (Turn your NFTs into pins!)

There are 1000 Reppin NFT passes in total. All passes are equal in utility and rarity:  
• 250 "GM"  
• 250 "Wagmi"  
• 250 "Probably Nothing"  
• 250 "HODL"

Rep what you HODL.
